## OpenSCAD on macOS ARM64

Qt runtime check fails on native ARM64. Fix: `Scad_Renderer.py` prepends `arch -x86_64` on `darwin/arm64`. Disable with `OPENSCAD_USE_ROSETTA=0`. Headless PNG needs Xvfb (`DISPLAY=:99`).
